<h1>Prime Pairs Plus</h1>

<p>This project was inspired by Matt Parker's Maths Puzzles series (see video below).</p>

<p>
  Order digits from
  <input type="number" id="min-term" min="1" value="1" class="narrow-input">
  to
  <input type="number" id="max-term" value="10" class="narrow-input">
</p>

<p>
  So that every
  <input type="number" id="tuple-length" value="2" class="narrow-input">
  numbers in a row add up to a
  <select name="filter" id="filter">
    <option value="prime">prime number</option>
    <option value="square">perfect square</option>
    <option value="fibonacci">Fibonacci number</option>
  </select>
</p>

<p id="solution"></p>

<div class="line-break"></div>

